    <item>
      <title>Erste 首席执行官批评奥地利对俄罗斯威胁掉以轻心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/russia-threat-is-being-ignored-by-austrians-erste-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利第一储蓄银行集团首席执行官彼得·博塞克批评称，奥地利民众似乎不太担心俄罗斯可能将对乌克兰的战争扩大到其他国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/russia-threat-is-being-ignored-by-austrians-erste-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国军机入侵后日本紧急出动战机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/japan-scrambles-fighters-after-chinese-military-plane-incursion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本紧急出动战斗机对周一短暂进入日本领空的中国军机进行警告，日本国内媒体称这是中国军机首次入侵日本领空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/japan-scrambles-fighters-after-chinese-military-plane-incursion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“美国制造”比特币威胁中国巨头比特大陆的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-s-made-in-usa-bitcoin-relies-on-chinese-rig-maker-bitmain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，一家中国公司一直主宰着加密货币领域最赚钱的领域之一。日益加剧的政治紧张局势以及唐纳德·特朗普重夺白宫的可能性，对这一统治构成了前所未有的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-s-made-in-usa-bitcoin-relies-on-chinese-rig-maker-bitmain</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
