    <item>
      <title>突尼斯领导人在十月投票前更换大部分内阁成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/tunisian-president-swaps-out-much-of-cabinet-before-october-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯总统更换了十几位政府部长，他称这是在十月份他很有可能获胜的选举之前打击腐败的“不可或缺的”举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/tunisian-president-swaps-out-much-of-cabinet-before-october-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪支持率在新民意调查中下滑，反对党领袖支持率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/modi-s-popularity-dips-in-new-poll-as-opposition-leader-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新调查显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪仍然是该国领导人最受欢迎的人选，尽管他的支持率稳步下降，而反对派的拉胡尔·甘地则支持这一结果，这与最近的选举结果基本一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/modi-s-popularity-dips-in-new-poll-as-opposition-leader-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:03:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾爆发抗议活动，警方瞄准杜特尔特牧师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/protests-erupt-in-philippines-as-police-target-duterte-s-pastor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，菲律宾南部城市达沃爆发暴力抗议活动，警方试图逮捕一名与前总统罗德里戈·杜特尔特家族有联系的福音派传教士，这加深了该强大家族与总统费迪南德·马科斯之间的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/protests-erupt-in-philippines-as-police-target-duterte-s-pastor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新规定使佐科威之子无法参加印尼大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/new-rules-shut-jokowi-s-son-out-of-indonesia-s-regional-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼选举委员会颁布了新规定，实际上终结了总统佐科·维多多的小儿子参加11月地区选举的任何机会，这一前景引发了上周的大规模抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/new-rules-shut-jokowi-s-son-out-of-indonesia-s-regional-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
